{"tid":1489681,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"想請教dark souls fans","createTime":"2019-08-20T02:31:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T01:29:29.000Z","uid":56911,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"dd5f77d3f4f78e5a130e32d42231aaf1328ecacf","tid":1489681,"uid":56911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:31:29.000Z","msg":"是咁的有少少野想請教<br />\n好耐之前玩過dark soul 1 同埋BB，太on99睇太多攻略，兩隻都無爆到機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但其實我真係幾鍾意玩喱類，我見dark souls 3 而定psn特價係咪好抵買？<br />\nDARK SOULS&trade; III - Deluxe Edition 應該係包dlc 兩隻 197.7HKD<br />\n<br />\n另外想問有無youtube睇dark soul 1,2既故事 ／ 打機片係好正既？<br />\n想知多d個故事，主要因為未必會玩返2了"},{"pid":"a7208d210db69763dfe35672300068deb94ecebe","tid":1489681,"uid":172889,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:27:38.000Z","msg":"去啦, Dark Souls 3 唔減價都買得過, 何況減價<br />\nDS 系列黎講佢算易入門, D boss 戰好正, 重玩性又高<br />\n<br />\n想睇人打+故事的話<br />\n香港channel 就睇東哥啦"},{"pid":"2ac37278fc4c66bf2b29cfd2aa8df6eaf58f0f9c","tid":1489681,"uid":172889,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:30:02.000Z","msg":"有心機有時間咪爆埋隻DS1 同BB囉<br />\n不過唔熟個節奏的話<br />\nBB D boss 戰會打得好辛苦 (特別係DLC 嗰堆) , 要有定心理準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9e0eec8ae364b7ea9b1544bca55fe5568e5457","tid":1489681,"uid":18082,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:09:54.000Z","msg":"睇Vaatividya"},{"pid":"3d59652ab6276a8a4f74ea5390aeb85cac9c60df","tid":1489681,"uid":30678,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:11:39.000Z","msg":"玩過1已經夠<br />\n2係黑歷史同主線冇關係"},{"pid":"4179f0781b678cce2d0fb0f50c661d8b3116c194","tid":1489681,"uid":127464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd5f77d3f4f78e5a130e32d42231aaf1328ecacf","tid":1489681,"uid":56911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:31:29.000Z","msg":"是咁的有少少野想請教<br />\n好耐之前玩過dark soul 1 同埋BB，太on99睇太多攻略，兩隻都無爆到機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但其實我真係幾鍾意玩喱類，我見dark souls 3 而定psn特價係咪好抵買？<br />\nDARK SOULS&trade; III - Deluxe Edition 應該係包dlc 兩隻 197.7HKD<br />\n<br />\n另外想問有無youtube睇dark soul 1,2既故事 ／ 打機片係好正既？<br />\n想知多d個故事，主要因為未必會玩返2了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:22:56.000Z","msg":"歡迎入番坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首推係 DS1 之後就直接可以DS3<br />\n兩個世界觀同設定係一樣 <br />\n當你玩哂之後可以試下玩埋 DS2&lt; 因為作者唔同 所以如果你依順序 1&gt;2&gt;3咁玩 <br />\n你玩到2會發現有小小難以理解劇情 因為2同 1,3 基本世界設定一定係有出入<br />\n所以建議你玩1&gt;3  玩完之後 第2集當佢外傳咁玩就好<br />\n此外 BB , Demon soul 都係當中好作品 但Demon soul太久遠 如果唔想玩可以上網睇人地打機片<br />\n可以係youtube 搜尋 阿東RangerEast 基本依類型game佢全部都有拍 <br />\n而且有大量資料分析+darksoul設定集資訊<br />\n另外都可以睇 陳兩儀 &lt; 都有大量ds片+資料 攻略 只係本人比較小睇"},{"pid":"0366a6a23a05e98dbd52333193b436dc373e3468","tid":1489681,"uid":85694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:24:00.000Z","msg":"識唔識英文<br />\n好多鬼佬做故事片"},{"pid":"e6308215d147b84d5fd8cb5f008490213ed9717b","tid":1489681,"uid":4237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:50:30.000Z","msg":"玩1 3 同bb夠<br />\n2 當興趣先玩"},{"pid":"eb3ccf5ddb6695b0abdac8c6f556f5b305edd100","tid":1489681,"uid":172889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1b9e0eec8ae364b7ea9b1544bca55fe5568e5457","tid":1489681,"uid":18082,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:09:54.000Z","msg":"睇Vaatividya"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:50:49.000Z","msg":"呢個高汁。<br />\n但自問英文差，每片最少要睇兩次。"},{"pid":"e78591bc17173d98ef0152a41132e17be0cc83e7","tid":1489681,"uid":92132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:24:03.000Z","msg":"最近玩緊BB  DS真係好想令人重玩<br />\n好想試下全法術/全咒術咁過關"},{"pid":"9c3b6a3917178e2fc8fac2091ecd58c47316de61","tid":1489681,"uid":110656,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:25:55.000Z","msg":"睇陳兩儀"},{"pid":"7998b332ccb252933823d8e4506c2f0239edeb48","tid":1489681,"uid":172889,"li